---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="Now - Johanna Sneed"
    description="What I'm currently working on, learning, and thinking about"
    type="website">
    <div class="page-container">
        <header class="now-header">
            <h1 class="section-title">What I'm doing now</h1>
            <p class="header-subtitle">Last updated: January 2026</p>
        </header>

        <main class="now-content">
            <section>
                <h2>Working on</h2>
                <p>I started a new job as a Digital Accessibility Delivery Lead in mid-2025, and I've been enjoying learning from experts in the field and learning more about how large scale organizations manage accessibility. I've also enjoyed stepping back into an individual contributor role. I loved formally leading others, but this works well for the current phase of my life.</p>
                <br>
                <p>I'm maintaining the <a href="https://userexperience.directory/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="intro-link">UX Research Directory</a> and <a href="https://www.figma.com/community/plugin/1479149610770303057/design-review-notes" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="intro-link">Design Review Notes plugin (which recently surpassed 100 users!)</a> </p>

                <br>
                <p>I am currently writing a book on incorporating resiliency into UX design practices. The process has been challenging but rewarding.</p>
            
              
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Hobbies</h2>
                <p>I've been diving into crafts, like beadwork to help with mindfulness and creativity.</p>
            
            </section>

            <section>
                <h2>Media</h2>
                <ul>
                <li>Reading: I've been reading a lot of technical books during the book writing process, so the list is long. Otherwise, trying to get through <i>Listen for the Lie</i></li>
                <li>Watching: Traitors!!</li>
                <li>Playing: Just starting Hades II, and my husband recently got me into WoW</li>

                </ul>
   
            </section>

            <section class="inspiration-section">
                <h2>About this page</h2>
                <p>
                    This page is inspired by <a href="https://nownownow.com/">nownownow.com</a>, a directory of people's "now" pages. 
                    It's a way to share what I'm currently focused on without maintaining a personal blog.
                </p>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .page-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    }

    .now-header {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
        padding-top: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .now-header h1 {
        margin: 0 0 var(--space-xs) 0;
    }

    .header-subtitle {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        color: var(--color-muted);
        margin: 0;
    }

    .now-content {
        display: grid;
        gap: var(--space-md);
        max-width: 65ch;
    }

    section h2 {
        font-family: var(--font-special);
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm) 0;
    }

    section ul {
        list-style: disc;
        margin: 0;
        padding-left: var(--space-lg);
    }

    section li {
        margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--color-fg);
    }

    section p {
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: var(--color-fg);
    }

    .inspiration-section {
        padding: var(--space-lg);
        border: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
        border-radius: var(--curve-sm);
        background-color: rgba(212, 57, 0, 0.03);
    }

    .inspiration-section a {
        color: var(--color-accent);
        text-decoration: underline;
        transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .inspiration-section a:hover,
    .inspiration-section a:focus-visible {
        color: var(--color-fg);
    }

    .inspiration-section a:focus-visible {
        outline: 2px solid var(--color-accent);
        outline-offset: 2px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .page-container {
            padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-sm);
        }

        section h2 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
        }
    }
</style>
